[[File:Reward casket (beginner) detail.png|left|130px]]
A '''[[reward casket]] (beginner)''' is received after completing the final clue of a [[Clue scroll (beginner)|beginner clue scroll]] trail, and contains the final reward for the trail.

While players can only have one of each type of clue scroll in their possession, they can possess unlimited amounts of reward caskets, and are eligible to receive clue scrolls again once it is obtained.

The beginner reward casket, unlike other reward caskets, cannot be opened on Entrana. If players attempt to do so, the chatbox will state "''You cannot open this on Entrana, the monks are watching you too closely.''" Furthermore, accounts that are less than 10 hours old will not be able to receive any unique rewards from these caskets.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1418876325192929281|date=24 July 2021|archiveurl=https://archive.is/tUgbR|archivedate=22:34, 29 July 2021 (UTC)|quote=10 hours, applies to all accounts doing beginner clues.}}

==Rewards==
Beginner clues generate a minimum of 1 reward and a maximum of 3, granting an average of 2 rewards per casket. The rewards consist of generic items, and items that are unique for beginner clues.

All droprates are confirmed by Mod Tide.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Tide|url=https://twitter.com/JagexTide/status/1182709121566564355|date=11 October 2019|archiveurl=https://archive.fo/kGxJb|archivedate=11 October 2019|quote=Hey guys and gals, i'ts been 6 months since the release of beginner clues so I thought you might like to see what the drop rates are! Enjoy those cabbages, they taste great.|name=Clue rates tweet}} The listed rarities are per roll.

The average loot roll is worth {{Coins|floor({{BeginnerClueValue}})}}. On average, beginner clues are worth {{Coins|floor(2 * {{BeginnerClueValue}})}}.

===Beginner clue uniques===
*The chance to receive any unique is 1/24 per roll, with a specific unique being 1/360 per roll. Players obtain an average of 1 unique per 12 clue scrolls, and a specific unique an average of once per 180 clue scrolls.

